</EMPH>

</BLOCK>

</ITEM>


<ITEM>

<BLOCK>

<EMPH slant = "italic">
Are you pregnant or think you might be?
</EMPH>

</BLOCK>

</ITEM>


<ITEM>

<BLOCK>

<EMPH slant = "italic">
Are you breastfeeding?
</EMPH>

</BLOCK>

</ITEM>


<ITEM>

